{
  "stem": "20848.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I went to the Schmidt that following night, or the same night.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Following night.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "To thank her for saving my life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And she-- I gave her such a speech in Czechoslovakian that she was a very hardened woman, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But she cried.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And she said to me, you can come back to work for me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I-- I have forgiven you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I worked for her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And then one day, again one Saturday-- I have to bring this up because this is a very important thing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "There was-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] because they say that the Jewish people went to-- to-- to death like lambs to slaughter, I have to bring this up.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "One Saturday, there was again the siren sounding and [GERMAN], [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, we're all in the block.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "That was during the day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, we heard shooting and shooting and shooting.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And heard terrible explosions.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And what happened was that the Sonderkommandos-- which only consisted of Jewish men-- you know what Sonderkommandos was?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They exploded a crematorium.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They made a revolt, an uprising.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They cut the wires, and they all ran away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They all ran away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and I think one crematorium exploded in-- in the-- the-- the one that was used mostly.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The one the closest, I-- I think, to the camp, was exploded, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And unfortunately, we heard later on that they were already captured.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And Chaim Kaminski was shot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's how Chaim Kaminski lost his life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was shot.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that was in the-- pardon?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, absolutely.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was part of the revolt.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's-- he-- he was a kapo there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He must have been the-- the-- the main person in the revolt or the uprising.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And after that, we were still in camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
